\c 14
\s Pauro naBharnabhasi paIkoniyamu neDhebhe neRistra
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika paIkoniyamu kuti vakapinda vose pamwechete musinagoge ravaJudha, vakataura nokudaro kuti vazhinji-zhinji vavaJudha navaGiriki vakatenda.
\v 2 Asi vaJudha vasina kutenda, vakamutsa moyo yavahedheni, vakaipisa moyo yavo kuti vavenge hama.
\v 3 Naizvozvo vakagarapo nguva refu, vachitaura vasingatyi munaShe; wakamupupurira kunyika shoko renyasha dzake, akavapa zviratidzo nezvishamiso kuti zviitwe namavoko avo.
\v 4 Asi chaunga cheguta chakapesana, vamwe vakabatirira kuvaJudha, vamwe kuvapositora.
\v 5 Zvino vahedheni, navaJudha, navabati vavo vakati vachivamukira nokuvataka namabwe;
\v 6 ivo vakazviziva, vakatizira Ristra neDerbe, aiva maguta eRikaonia, nokunyika yakapoteredza;
\v 7 ipapo vakaparidzira evhangeri.
\v 8 Zvino paRistra paigara mumwe murume wakanga asinesimba patsoka dzake, ari chirema kubva padumbu ramai vake, asina kutongofamba.
\v 9 Iye wakanzwa Pauro achitaura; zvino iye akamutarisisa, akavona kuti unokutenda kuti aporeswe,
\v 10 akati nenzwi guru: Mira kwazvo netsoka dzako, iye akavhazuka akafamba.
\v 11 Zvino chunga chakati chavona zvakaitwa naPauro, vakasimudza manzwi avo norurimi rwavaRikaonia, vachiti: Vamwari vaburukira kwatiri vakaita savanhu.
\v 12 Bharnabhasi vakamutumidza Zeusi, naPauro Hemesi, nokuti ndiye waiva mutauri mukuru.
\v 13 Ipapo muprista waZeusi waiva pamberi peguta, akavuya pamasuvo nenzombe namaruva okushonga, achida kuita chibayiro nechaunga, anavanhu vazhinji naye.
\v 14 Zvino vapositora Bharnabhasi naPauro vakati vachinzwa, vakabvarura nguvo dzavo, vakamhanyira pakati pavanhu vazhinji, vachidanidzira.
\v 15 vachiti: Varume, munoitireiko zvinhu izvi? Nesu tiri vanhu vane manzwiro mamwe nemwivo; tinokuparidzirai mashoko akanaka, kuti mubve panaizvozvo zvisinamaturo, mutendevukire kunaMwari mupenyu wakaita denga napasi, negungwa, nezvose zviri mukati mazvo.
\v 16 Iye, panguva dzakapfuvura wakatendera vahedheni vose kufamba nenzira dzavo.
\v 17 Asi haana kuzvisiya asina uchapupu, pakuti wakaita zvakanaka, achitipa mvura yokudenga, nenguva dzezviyo zvizhinji, achizadza moyo yenyu nezvokudya nomufaro.
\v 18 Nokutaura kwavo saizvozvo, vakatambura kwazvo kudzivisa vanhu kuti varege kuvabayira.
\v 19 Ipapo vaJudha vakabva Andiyokiya neIkoniyamu, vakasvika, vakamutsa moyo yavanhu vazhinji, vakataka Pauro namabwe, vakamukwevera kunze kweguta vachiti wafa.
\v 20 Asi vadzidzi vakati vamukomba, iye akasimuka, akapinda muguta. Fume mangwana akaenda Dhebhe naBharnabhasi.
\v 21 Vakati vaparidza evhangeri paguta iro, vakaita vadzidzi vazhinji, ndokudzokera Ristra, neIkoniyamu, neAndiyokiya,
\v 22 vachisimbisa mweya yavadzidzi, vachivaraira kuti vatsungirire pakutenda, vachiti, tinofanira kupinda vushe bwaMwari namatambudziko mazhinji.
\v 23 Vakavasanangurira vakuru pakereke imwe neimwe, vakanyengetera, vachitsanya, vakavaisa kunaShe, wavaitenda.
\v 24 Vakagura nePisidhiya, ndokusvika Pamfiria.
\v 25 Vakati vaparidza shoko paPerga, vakaburukira Ataria.
\v 26 Vakabvapo, vakaenda Andiyokiya nechikepe, apo pavakanga vaiswa panyasha dzaMwari kubata basa ravakanga vapedzisa zvino.
\v 27 Vakati vasvika, vakavunganidza kereke, vakarondedzera zvose zvakanga zvaitwa naMwari navo, uye kuti wakanga azarurira vahedheni mukova wokutenda.
\v 28 Vakagara nguva huru navadzidzi.
